O. A. LA BUDDE, Collector, etc., v. NORTHERN PAPER MILLS. No. 5690. Circuit Court of Appeals, Seventh Circuit. March 5, 1936.

Before EVANS and SPARKS, Circuit Judges, and LINDLEY, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

On motion of counsel for appellee, it is now here ordered adjudged and decreed by this court that this appeal be, and the same is hereby, dismissed.
